277
00:21:52,619 --> 00:21:54,420
and harassing the others.

278
00:21:56,619 --> 00:21:57,690
Gyeo Rye.

279
00:21:58,859 --> 00:22:02,890
I was only joking around...

280
00:22:03,529 --> 00:22:07,900
since I don't have many happy memories of that room.

281
00:22:11,170 --> 00:22:12,240
Well, anyway.

282
00:22:13,970 --> 00:22:16,240
I need to go and catch that ghost.

283
00:22:17,769 --> 00:22:18,940
I'll call you again.

284
00:22:22,109 --> 00:22:25,250
That punk. He actually believed it.

285
00:22:25,849 --> 00:22:28,750
(Gyeo Rye)

286
00:23:54,599 --> 00:23:55,740
(Room 403)

287
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,970
Those who hesitate...

288
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,670
always lose.

289
00:24:35,809 --> 00:24:39,950
You wouldn't be hesitating either if you had learned from me properly.

290
00:24:45,420 --> 00:24:46,460
I told you...

291
00:24:48,490 --> 00:24:52,359
to leave quickly without causing any trouble.

292
00:24:53,130 --> 00:24:56,499
I can live like trash...

293
00:24:56,500 --> 00:24:58,740
as you had wished.

294
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:08,249
Nobody wants this, Gyeo Rye.

295
00:25:08,250 --> 00:25:09,949
You won't get better. Don't do it.

296
00:25:09,950 --> 00:25:11,149
You've done well so far.

297
00:25:11,150 --> 00:25:13,150
- Gyeo Rye. - Yoon Gyeo Rye. Don't do it.

298
00:25:23,589 --> 00:25:25,730
What? You can't...

299
00:25:26,630 --> 00:25:27,960
even kill me?

300
00:25:33,299 --> 00:25:34,299
No.

301
00:25:35,309 --> 00:25:37,309
I can't. Scratch that.

302
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:40,240
I won't kill you.

303
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:43,579
You know,

304
00:25:44,309 --> 00:25:45,319
I...

305
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:48,890
won't live like you, scumbag.

306
00:25:49,349 --> 00:25:52,160
The real scumbag is Kang Tae Sik.

307
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:56,960
I can't let him die as a good man.

308
00:25:57,859 --> 00:26:00,900
That jerk tried to kill me.

309
00:26:01,559 --> 00:26:02,970
It's clearly a crime.

310
00:26:05,170 --> 00:26:07,970
But Kang Tae Sik's biggest crime...

311
00:26:08,670 --> 00:26:10,809
is trying to steal someone else's son.

312
00:26:12,809 --> 00:26:15,809
How dare he steal my son?

313
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:18,180
So he must be punished.

314
00:26:19,750 --> 00:26:21,079
Who stole your son?

315
00:26:21,690 --> 00:26:23,190
Mr. Kang?

316
00:26:24,150 --> 00:26:25,160
No, he didn't.

317
00:26:25,890 --> 00:26:27,519
You threw away your son.

318
00:26:28,019 --> 00:26:29,890
No. That day.

319
00:26:30,789 --> 00:26:34,460
The day I ran away from you,

320
00:26:36,430 --> 00:26:37,869
your son died.

321
00:26:39,799 --> 00:26:41,710
Whatever. Take this...

322
00:26:42,609 --> 00:26:43,609
to the police.

323
00:26:44,569 --> 00:26:46,279
Report Kang Tae Sik yourself.

324
00:26:47,109 --> 00:26:48,710
Then, I will forgive him.

325
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:52,980
And even leave this place quietly.

326
00:26:59,390 --> 00:27:00,420
Yoon Gyeo Rye!

327
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:03,230
Even if you don't do it,

328
00:27:04,230 --> 00:27:06,599
it will be the end of Kang Tae Sik if I do.

329
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:09,299
But if you make the call,

330
00:27:09,970 --> 00:27:11,769
the old folks...

331
00:27:12,170 --> 00:27:14,700
and the nurse in this hospital...

332
00:27:15,339 --> 00:27:18,880
will not be accused of confining me.

333
00:27:19,079 --> 00:27:20,279
You hear me, Gyeo Rye?

334
00:27:22,380 --> 00:27:23,809
Don't call my name.

335
00:27:25,950 --> 00:27:27,980
Don't you dare call my name.

336
00:27:39,799 --> 00:27:41,059
(Room 403)

337
00:27:44,970 --> 00:27:48,039
He should repay my kindness of bringing him into this world.

338
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,259
Are you not eating?

339
00:28:15,630 --> 00:28:16,730
Great timing.

340
00:28:17,430 --> 00:28:20,240
I'm tired of hospital food. I want to eat...

341
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,769
something outside in secret.

342
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:27,940
At a restaurant.

343
00:28:38,690 --> 00:28:42,029
To tell you the truth, ox bone soup is my favourite.

344
00:28:48,730 --> 00:28:49,970
Now that hits it.

345
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:56,069
Was it Jun Kyung?

346
00:28:56,210 --> 00:28:57,440
Yes.

347
00:28:57,710 --> 00:28:58,740
Jun Kyung.

348
00:29:01,039 --> 00:29:02,079
What's your wish?

349
00:29:04,750 --> 00:29:08,720
Don't you only grant the wishes of those on the verge of death?

350
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:14,920
From what I see, you're living to die.

351
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:23,130
By any chance, is your wish...

352
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:26,768
to become a family with Gyeo Rye and live with him forever?

353
00:29:26,769 --> 00:29:30,240
Or to be loved by him?

354
00:29:32,309 --> 00:29:33,410
It's none of the two.

355
00:29:34,380 --> 00:29:35,450
Then what is it?

356
00:29:37,980 --> 00:29:42,150
To never get abandoned by my family again.

357
00:29:46,759 --> 00:29:48,190
That's my real wish.

358
00:29:50,390 --> 00:29:51,529
If I don't die.

359
00:30:01,339 --> 00:30:04,339
(New Hope Orphanage)

360
00:30:10,410 --> 00:30:12,049
It's okay. Let's go.

361
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:17,819
(New Hope Orphanage)

362
00:30:19,589 --> 00:30:21,119
So Yoon Gyeo Rye...

363
00:30:22,089 --> 00:30:23,759
