364
00:30:24,690 --> 00:30:26,329
Are you going after him?

365
00:30:27,059 --> 00:30:29,099
Is that why you kept visiting me?

366
00:30:35,509 --> 00:30:37,269
I wondered if I could become happy...

367
00:30:38,779 --> 00:30:39,910
if I were with you.

368
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:48,920
Yoon Gyeo Rye.

369
00:30:50,089 --> 00:30:51,750
I've never seen him like that.

370
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:55,759
Aren't you...

371
00:30:56,630 --> 00:31:00,059
and that sharp-tempered nurse the ones who changed him?

372
00:31:18,180 --> 00:31:19,420
Take a look at this.

373
00:31:20,180 --> 00:31:21,279
What is it?

374
00:31:26,019 --> 00:31:31,160
(3 Adults Killed in Fire at Senam Apartments)

375
00:31:34,329 --> 00:31:37,969
(A 6-year-old girl survived in the Senam Apartments fire)

376
00:31:37,970 --> 00:31:40,099
(A possible arson in Senam Apartments, Beomeun-dong)

377
00:31:42,309 --> 00:31:44,909
(A single mother saved her 6-year-old child...)

378
00:31:44,910 --> 00:31:47,579
(in the Senam Apartments fire even as her body was burning.)

379
00:31:53,150 --> 00:31:54,220
Yes.

380
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:57,619
Your mother...

381
00:31:58,220 --> 00:32:00,720
had passed away after hugging you so tightly...

382
00:32:02,529 --> 00:32:05,960
in that blazing fire, leaving you without...

383
00:32:07,529 --> 00:32:09,069
a single burn on your body.

384
00:32:10,829 --> 00:32:13,470
The adults thought the truth would hurt you...

385
00:32:14,500 --> 00:32:16,670
and give you a hard time once you grew up,

386
00:32:19,910 --> 00:32:21,809
so they kept it from you.

387
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:28,578
Gosh. Why would anyone leave such a pretty girl?

388
00:32:28,579 --> 00:32:30,518
So what if she's pretty? She's an orphan, anyway.

389
00:32:30,519 --> 00:32:33,259
- She's pretty but an orphan. - Poor Jun Kyung.

390
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:37,029
Your family...

391
00:32:38,359 --> 00:32:40,960
never abandoned you from the beginning.

392
00:32:44,529 --> 00:32:45,599
Jun Kyung.

393
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:48,000
You were...

394
00:32:49,410 --> 00:32:51,309
a precious daughter your mother...

395
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:53,980
risked her life to protect.

396
00:32:58,049 --> 00:32:59,880
So can't you live...

397
00:33:02,190 --> 00:33:04,589
your life to the fullest...

398
00:33:08,119 --> 00:33:09,829
for the sake of your mother?

399
00:33:15,700 --> 00:33:18,368
(A single mom in her 20s died but saved her 6-year-old daughter.)

400
00:33:18,369 --> 00:33:20,469
(A single mother saved her 6-year-old child...)

401
00:33:20,470 --> 00:33:22,539
(in the Senam Apartments fire even as her body was burning.)

402
00:33:41,490 --> 00:33:42,690
(A 6-year-old girl survived in the Senam Apartments fire)

403
00:33:46,329 --> 00:33:48,429
(The cause of the Senam Apartments fire...)

404
00:33:48,430 --> 00:33:50,529
(was a joint suicide attempt using a briquette.)

405
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:53,839
Seok Jun?

406
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:56,410
(Only an 8-year-old son of a family survived)

407
00:33:58,470 --> 00:34:00,279
Why is Seok Jun here?

408
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:28,599
Straighten up so I can take a photo.

409
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:31,070
Okay, here I go.

410
00:34:32,039 --> 00:34:35,280
Look at the camera. 1, 2, 3.

411
00:34:37,909 --> 00:34:39,380
(New Hope Orphanage)

412
00:34:47,019 --> 00:34:49,559
Let's go, Jun Kyung.

413
00:34:50,730 --> 00:34:51,889
It's okay.

414
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,329
You too, Seok Jun.

415
00:34:57,869 --> 00:34:59,138
(New Hope Orphanage)

416
00:34:59,139 --> 00:35:00,869
You can't call it a joint suicide.

417
00:35:01,739 --> 00:35:03,639
I heard the guy made him take the drug.

418
00:35:04,210 --> 00:35:07,039
That's right. The kid never agreed to it.

419
00:35:07,639 --> 00:35:10,380
I feel really bad for Jun Kyung.

420
00:35:10,579 --> 00:35:13,619
Her relatives didn't want her. So she ended up here.

421
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:17,750
Oh, right. Some newspaper company...

422
00:35:17,849 --> 00:35:19,619
is coming to interview them later.

423
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:23,760
- Yes. We're going to take a photo. - Do you want this?

424
00:35:24,860 --> 00:35:28,360
Seriously. I feel sorry for the kids.

425
00:36:15,809 --> 00:36:17,110
Dig in.

426
00:36:26,090 --> 00:36:27,190
Lies.

427
00:36:29,460 --> 00:36:30,630
Those are all lies.

428
00:36:31,860 --> 00:36:33,860
What do I...

429
00:36:36,530 --> 00:36:37,829
I'm borrowing your phone.

430
00:36:49,079 --> 00:36:51,110
I can't remember his number.

431
00:36:54,579 --> 00:36:55,849
What was it?

432
00:36:56,519 --> 00:36:57,650
Come on.

433
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:03,389
(Calls)

434
00:37:06,030 --> 00:37:07,359
(Gyeo Rye)

435
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:11,130
Okay. 0104465890.

436
00:37:11,269 --> 00:37:12,800
Remember 0104465...

437
00:37:30,750 --> 00:37:31,820
Gosh.

438
00:37:33,590 --> 00:37:35,320
Life sure is hard.

439
00:37:49,170 --> 00:37:52,610
Mister, please hurry. Please.

440
00:38:07,090 --> 00:38:08,860
(Jerk Seok Jun)

441
00:38:13,199 --> 00:38:15,828
- Answer it. Please. - The person you have reached...

442
00:38:15,829 --> 00:38:18,469
is not available. Please try again later.

443
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,400
(From: Jerk Seok Jun)

444
00:38:20,401 --> 00:38:22,840
I'll grant your wish.

445
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:24,570
See you above.

446
00:38:24,969 --> 00:38:27,840
I'll make you smile up there.

447
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:49,030
(New Text Message)

448
00:38:50,230 --> 00:38:52,230
(Seok Jun is...)

449
00:39:01,739 --> 00:39:03,980
The hospital.

450
00:39:21,630 --> 00:39:23,969
Seok Jun is going to the hospital to kill you.

451
00:39:24,269 --> 00:39:25,429
Avoid him at any cost.

452
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:28,500
I'm sorry about everything.

453
00:39:58,329 --> 00:40:01,900
It's Yoon Gyeo Rye. Wait there. I'm on my way.

454
00:40:02,039 --> 00:40:04,539
(It's Yoon Gyeo Rye. Wait there. I'm on my way.)

455
00:40:49,550 --> 00:40:51,590
(Yoon Ki Chun)

456
00:41:03,199 --> 00:41:04,199
Hello?

457
00:41:04,469 --> 00:41:07,699
Mr. Kang. Long time no see.

458
00:41:08,039 --> 00:41:10,539
When are you coming back? I have something to say.

459
00:41:11,469 --> 00:41:12,539
I miss you.

460
00:41:14,679 --> 00:41:16,610
Why do you miss me?

461
00:41:17,309 --> 00:41:18,809
Where do you want to see me?

462
00:41:18,980 --> 00:41:21,880
Where else? Woori Hospital, obviously.

463
00:41:22,690 --> 00:41:23,750
What?

464
00:41:25,090 --> 00:41:26,320
Woori Hospital?

465
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:29,289
Didn't Gyeo Rye tell you?

466
00:41:29,889 --> 00:41:32,030
The man in the last room on the fourth floor is me.

467
00:41:32,530 --> 00:41:34,428
I almost died after you hit me with a rock...

468
00:41:34,429 --> 00:41:36,769
on my head.

469
00:41:36,969 --> 00:41:39,070
Then the nurses and elders here...

470
00:41:39,269 --> 00:41:42,439
were afraid you'd become a murderer,

471
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:43,969
so they hid me here and saved me.

472
00:41:44,670 --> 00:41:45,739
What are you talking about?

473
00:41:46,110 --> 00:41:49,079
All that went to nothing.

474
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,980
They shouldn't have kept me alive.

475
00:41:51,780 --> 00:41:54,849
Gyeo Rye and I caught up after 20 years.

476
00:41:55,150 --> 00:41:58,989
Now, it's time to meet you, Mr... I mean, Captain Kang.

477
00:41:59,559 --> 00:42:01,589
For smashing my head...

478
00:42:01,590 --> 00:42:03,090
and taking my son away from me,

479
00:42:03,929 --> 00:42:06,199
you need to be punished.

480
00:42:06,500 --> 00:42:07,829
Yoon Ki Chun.

481
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:12,670
Don't you dare do anything to people in the hospital or Gyeo Rye.

482
00:42:13,199 --> 00:42:14,440
If you do anything,

483
00:42:15,769 --> 00:42:17,670
I'm going to kill you.

484
00:42:18,340 --> 00:42:19,409
Hello?

485
00:42:20,210 --> 00:42:21,980
I'm his father.

486
00:42:23,250 --> 00:42:25,280
He's my son.

487
00:42:26,250 --> 00:42:29,119
How dare you? You've always been arrogant...

488
00:42:29,519 --> 00:42:31,989
since the moment I met you.

489
00:42:32,389 --> 00:42:34,389
Everyone is deceived.

490
00:42:35,059 --> 00:42:38,360
Don't you dare do anything.

491
00:42:39,130 --> 00:42:40,360
Get it, you jerk?

492
00:42:44,500 --> 00:42:45,900
Crazy scumbag.

493
00:42:49,409 --> 00:42:51,210
(Taxi)

494
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:52,469
Taxi.

495
00:42:57,650 --> 00:42:59,049
Icheon please.

496
00:42:59,050 --> 00:43:00,420
Okay.

497
00:43:12,030 --> 00:43:13,260
How dare you?

498
00:43:13,860 --> 00:43:16,070
Do you know who I am?

499
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:17,800
Hey.

500
00:43:19,500 --> 00:43:22,908
Please leave Tae Sik alone.

501
00:43:22,909 --> 00:43:25,408
Why do you keep bothering him?

502
00:43:25,409 --> 00:43:28,738
You brainwashed the innocent man...

503
00:43:28,739 --> 00:43:30,249
and took advantage of him.

504
00:43:30,250 --> 00:43:31,349
Took advantage of him?

505
00:43:32,980 --> 00:43:36,420
We've known each other for 30 years.

506
00:43:36,889 --> 00:43:38,249
- I'm here alone... - You should stay inside.

507
00:43:38,250 --> 00:43:41,920
because I missed my friend.

508
00:43:42,420 --> 00:43:44,459
Keep your trap closed if you don't know anything.

509
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:45,730
My goodness, sir.

510
00:43:45,929 --> 00:43:48,529
How could you do this?

511
00:43:48,530 --> 00:43:50,569
Stop it already.

512
00:43:50,570 --> 00:43:52,098
How mean.

513
00:43:52,099 --> 00:43:54,670
Leave before I call the police.

514
00:43:54,940 --> 00:43:58,369
Captain Kang's out of town!

515
00:43:58,510 --> 00:44:01,238
He doesn't want to see you again.

516
00:44:01,239 --> 00:44:02,879
Leave for goodness' sake.

517
00:44:02,880 --> 00:44:05,209
How strange.

518
00:44:05,210 --> 00:44:08,550
Why is he never here every time I visit him?

519
00:44:08,980 --> 00:44:11,690
Isn't he strange? People say they see him all the time here.

520
00:44:12,250 --> 00:44:13,260
Everyone.

521
00:44:14,059 --> 00:44:16,659
Don't fall for that pretentious man.

522
00:44:16,760 --> 00:44:19,030
Mind your own business.

523
00:44:19,329 --> 00:44:22,929
You don't even have much time left. Don't waste your time like this.

524
00:44:23,699 --> 00:44:24,769
Oh, no.

525
00:44:26,300 --> 00:44:27,340
Why...

526
00:44:29,099 --> 00:44:30,710
Is this why you made me run errands?

527
00:44:33,440 --> 00:44:35,538
Did you make me go out and run errands...

528
00:44:35,539 --> 00:44:38,650
every time he made a fuss in here?

529
00:44:39,579 --> 00:44:43,150
Why on earth did you do that?

530
00:44:43,420 --> 00:44:44,489
For someone like me!

531
00:44:52,360 --> 00:44:53,400
Yoon Ki Chun.

532
00:44:54,300 --> 00:44:55,730
Why do you keep chasing me...

533
00:44:56,769 --> 00:44:59,738
and bothering me my whole life?

534
00:44:59,739 --> 00:45:00,800
And...

535
00:45:01,800 --> 00:45:02,869
why me?

536
00:45:07,039 --> 00:45:08,940
When tigers and lions...

537
00:45:09,780 --> 00:45:10,809
are hungry,

538
00:45:11,710 --> 00:45:13,119
they look for a prey.

539
00:45:14,349 --> 00:45:16,919
Sometimes they kill...

540
00:45:16,920 --> 00:45:18,650
the one that is left behind or looks weak,

541
00:45:19,690 --> 00:45:22,789
but sometimes they kill the one that's closest to them.

542
00:45:23,260 --> 00:45:27,929
Do you know what we call that?

543
00:45:30,570 --> 00:45:31,570
Ill-fated relationship.

544
00:45:36,670 --> 00:45:39,579
This place is a jackpot.

545
00:45:39,780 --> 00:45:41,110
They're all left behind...

546
00:45:41,210 --> 00:45:43,609
- and look weak. - My goodness.

547
00:45:43,610 --> 00:45:44,678
Come here!

548
00:45:44,679 --> 00:45:46,150
- Let me go. - My goodness.

549
00:45:47,079 --> 00:45:48,118
- Hey. - Come here, you jerk.

550
00:45:48,119 --> 00:45:49,589
Tae Sik. What are you doing?

551
00:45:49,590 --> 00:45:51,919
- Follow me, you jerk! - Hey.

552
00:45:51,920 --> 00:45:53,189
Stop it. You're so scary!

553
00:45:53,190 --> 00:45:55,460
- Come here! - Gosh.

554
00:45:56,090 --> 00:45:57,558
What's wrong with you?

555
00:45:57,559 --> 00:46:00,599
What? Are you embarrassed...

556
00:46:00,760 --> 00:46:02,329
to lose to a weak cancer patient?

557
00:46:02,800 --> 00:46:06,030
Did you really think people avoided you because you're scary?

558
00:46:06,800 --> 00:46:08,170
If they get involved with you,

559
00:46:08,969 --> 00:46:11,439
they were afraid they'd end up smelling like you too.

560
00:46:11,440 --> 00:46:13,979
I thought we were friends. Watch your mouth.

561
00:46:13,980 --> 00:46:17,380
Yes. I only stayed next to you...

562
00:46:18,150 --> 00:46:21,979
because I wanted to be successful.

563
00:46:21,980 --> 00:46:24,719
Did you think I was afraid of your power?

564
00:46:25,090 --> 00:46:26,519
You scumbag!

565
00:46:26,690 --> 00:46:30,030
Hey, Tae Sik. Stop it.

566
00:46:30,289 --> 00:46:32,730
- Stop it now. - Crazy prick.

567
00:46:34,829 --> 00:46:37,329
Hey. That hurts.

568
00:46:38,030 --> 00:46:40,570
Hey. Stop.

569
00:46:40,670 --> 00:46:42,969
Stop what?

570
00:46:43,670 --> 00:46:45,369
You crazy prick.

571
00:46:47,039 --> 00:46:48,139
I don't mind...

572
00:46:49,210 --> 00:46:51,309
because I was a fool,

573
00:46:52,110 --> 00:46:55,750
but don't bring in innocent people because of me.

574
00:46:56,349 --> 00:46:58,619
Get it? For goodness' sake.

575
00:47:01,489 --> 00:47:02,519
Please.

576
00:47:03,659 --> 00:47:04,760
Don't get other people involved...

577
00:47:05,659 --> 00:47:07,400
because of me.

578
00:47:08,300 --> 00:47:10,369
I won't forgive you for that.

579
00:47:12,230 --> 00:47:14,570
Hey. Help.

580
00:47:15,070 --> 00:47:16,710
Help me.

581
00:47:18,110 --> 00:47:20,409
Hey! Kang Tae Sik.

582
00:47:27,449 --> 00:47:31,050
That's why you can't be successful.

583
00:47:31,349 --> 00:47:33,019
I bet you didn't know about this.

584
00:48:13,300 --> 00:48:15,960
If he turns himself in with all the elders here,

585
00:48:16,530 --> 00:48:17,530
who knows?

586
00:48:20,500 --> 00:48:22,539
The video I just sent you is the proof.

587
00:48:34,750 --> 00:48:36,618
Hey, Tae Sik. Stop it.

588
00:48:36,619 --> 00:48:39,889
That knife won't do anything.

589
00:48:41,019 --> 00:48:44,329
I only took it out to provoke him.

590
00:48:47,429 --> 00:48:49,129
I recorded him...

591
00:48:49,130 --> 00:48:50,969
going frantic.

592
00:48:51,469 --> 00:48:52,530
So,

593
00:48:53,639 --> 00:48:55,599
go turn yourself in.

594
00:48:57,039 --> 00:49:00,110
Then I will leave quietly.

595
00:49:03,079 --> 00:49:04,110
(Icheon Police Station Detective Park)

596
00:49:07,219 --> 00:49:09,349
(Icheon Police Station Detective Park)

597
00:49:11,289 --> 00:49:12,389
Hello?

598
00:49:15,059 --> 00:49:17,289
I'm almost there.

599
00:49:27,170 --> 00:49:29,469
I've thought about it.

600
00:49:30,309 --> 00:49:32,510
I think I'd need more concrete evidence.

601
00:49:33,610 --> 00:49:35,340
I'll call you back.

602
00:49:36,349 --> 00:49:37,750
Yes, I'm sorry.

603
00:49:46,219 --> 00:49:50,059
(Icheon Police Station)

604
00:49:58,929 --> 00:50:00,340
(Move to trash)

605
00:50:03,309 --> 00:50:04,339
(Move to trash)

606
00:50:04,340 --> 00:50:05,409
(No photos or videos)

607
00:50:20,719 --> 00:50:22,619
(Mr. Kang)

608
00:50:29,699 --> 00:50:31,869
- Mr. Kang. - Yes, Nurse Seo.

609
00:50:32,530 --> 00:50:34,768
Where are you? I'm...

610
00:50:34,769 --> 00:50:38,369
I'm sorry I didn't visit you.

611
00:50:39,670 --> 00:50:41,138
I tried to visit you...

612
00:50:41,139 --> 00:50:43,849
So where are you right now?

613
00:50:46,250 --> 00:50:48,250
Something came up in the hospital.

614
00:50:49,579 --> 00:50:52,389
I'll visit you once this resolves.

615
00:50:53,050 --> 00:50:54,090
Yoon Ki Chun.

616
00:50:56,159 --> 00:50:58,289
He called me and told me.

617
00:50:58,829 --> 00:51:01,960
Did he blackmail you?

618
00:51:06,469 --> 00:51:07,539
He did.

619
00:51:08,599 --> 00:51:10,110
Whatever he said,

620
00:51:10,639 --> 00:51:12,639
don't be swayed. Understand?

621
00:51:13,139 --> 00:51:14,780
He can even kill people...

622
00:51:14,940 --> 00:51:16,750
with the things he says.

623
00:51:20,880 --> 00:51:23,389
This is between me and him.

624
00:51:23,619 --> 00:51:25,519
He's not trying to start a fight.

625
00:51:27,460 --> 00:51:28,719
He just wants to play.

626
00:51:29,590 --> 00:51:30,960
He's lonely.

627
00:51:32,559 --> 00:51:34,699
He became a monster because he's lonely.

628
00:51:35,099 --> 00:51:36,230
So...

629
00:51:38,329 --> 00:51:39,469
Yeon Joo.

630
00:51:39,800 --> 00:51:41,070
Yes, Father.

631
00:51:41,969 --> 00:51:44,909
Don't do anything for me.

632
00:51:46,170 --> 00:51:47,510
I'm begging you.

633
00:51:48,840 --> 00:51:49,949
Understand?

634
00:52:17,440 --> 00:52:23,110
(Death isn't the end to all.)

635
00:52:54,909 --> 00:52:56,210
Gosh.

636
00:53:27,679 --> 00:53:28,709
Gyeo Rye.

637
00:53:28,710 --> 00:53:30,750
Yes. Where are you?

638
00:53:31,250 --> 00:53:34,949
I'm on my way home.

639
00:53:36,079 --> 00:53:37,289
Where are you?

640
00:53:37,889 --> 00:53:38,920
Hospital.

641
00:53:42,260 --> 00:53:44,559
It's late. Why are you still up?

642
00:53:47,730 --> 00:53:48,760
Nothing.

643
00:54:07,849 --> 00:54:08,880
Gyeo Rye.

644
00:54:09,849 --> 00:54:12,650
Yoon Ki Chun will leave tomorrow.

645
00:54:14,719 --> 00:54:16,659
He wouldn't just leave quietly.

646
00:54:18,329 --> 00:54:19,488
I doubt it.

647
00:54:19,489 --> 00:54:22,199
I don't know if he's leaving on his own or forced to leave,

648
00:54:22,929 --> 00:54:24,699
but it seems something must've come up in Seoul.

649
00:54:24,869 --> 00:54:26,570
I heard him talking on the phone.

650
00:54:36,610 --> 00:54:37,849
So, Gyeo Rye.

651
00:54:39,179 --> 00:54:42,119
Don't do anything tonight.

652
00:54:43,550 --> 00:54:46,150
Okay.

653
00:54:47,059 --> 00:54:50,260
Gyeo Rye. I'm begging you.

654
00:54:51,829 --> 00:54:52,929
Okay?

655
00:54:53,960 --> 00:54:55,030
Okay.

656
00:55:04,510 --> 00:55:06,980
(Sonny, I will never forget you.)

657
00:55:51,849 --> 00:55:53,760
Thank you for staying alive.

658
00:55:54,420 --> 00:55:56,489
I knew you'd be here.

659
00:55:56,730 --> 00:55:59,189
But Kang Tae Sik kept insisting.

660
00:55:59,190 --> 00:56:02,159
It's true. He didn't know I was here.

661
00:56:02,300 --> 00:56:04,768
The elders and the nurse were terrified...

662
00:56:04,769 --> 00:56:07,940
something might happen to him, so they locked me up in here.

663
00:56:09,070 --> 00:56:10,670
Let's go. It's a long story.

664
00:56:20,449 --> 00:56:21,449
Okay.

665
00:56:25,949 --> 00:56:27,159
Chairman Yoon.

666
00:56:27,760 --> 00:56:29,659
Will that morphine be good money?

667
00:56:29,960 --> 00:56:31,630
It's not even hallucinatory.

668
00:56:31,659 --> 00:56:34,760
You think that's for sale?

669
00:56:35,130 --> 00:56:36,500
Then what is it for?

670
00:56:38,070 --> 00:56:40,269
To kick someone out from here,

671
00:56:40,670 --> 00:56:42,199
that needs to disappear.

672
00:56:44,269 --> 00:56:49,440
(Room 403)

673
00:56:58,849 --> 00:57:00,119
You should've...

674
00:57:00,219 --> 00:57:03,360
spread the rumour more actively.

675
00:57:04,260 --> 00:57:07,260
Now, you will be...

676
00:57:07,659 --> 00:57:11,199
my son's second victim.

677
00:57:31,090 --> 00:57:33,789
(We won't let your hand go.)

678
00:57:43,829 --> 00:57:45,499
Detective Park. This is Seo Yeon Joo...

679
00:57:45,500 --> 00:57:47,070
from Woori Hospice Hospital. We were supposed to meet today.

680
00:57:47,900 --> 00:57:50,570
I told you to turn yourself in. Why are you doing this?

681
00:57:50,639 --> 00:57:51,670
Let me go.

682
00:57:53,539 --> 00:57:56,039
You said you want my son to be happy.

683
00:57:57,150 --> 00:58:00,780
I'm going to find a way for everyone to be happy.

684
00:58:01,579 --> 00:58:03,178
That's what he really wants.

685
00:58:03,179 --> 00:58:04,719
He's my blood.

686
00:58:04,920 --> 00:58:06,749
I know what he really wants.

687
00:58:06,750 --> 00:58:07,789
Didn't you know?

688
00:58:08,360 --> 00:58:11,189
He said he got rid of all your blood when he donated his blood.

689
00:58:11,190 --> 00:58:12,789
I knew...

690
00:58:13,030 --> 00:58:15,158
talking won't work...

691
00:58:15,159 --> 00:58:16,260
Get your hand off!

692
00:58:19,570 --> 00:58:20,670
Mr. Kang.

693
00:58:24,269 --> 00:58:25,369
You...

694
00:58:26,639 --> 00:58:28,139
You're really out of your mind.

695
00:58:33,480 --> 00:58:34,480
Mr. Kang.

696
00:58:36,380 --> 00:58:39,119
Yes. Forget about everything,

697
00:58:40,389 --> 00:58:41,460
and let's have fun.

698
00:58:43,420 --> 00:58:46,690
Let's have fun together after death.

699
00:58:46,829 --> 00:58:48,429
- Mr. Kang. - Stay out.

700
00:58:48,659 --> 00:58:52,369
This is what you want from me.

701
00:58:53,070 --> 00:58:54,340
- No. - Isn't it?

702
00:59:00,139 --> 00:59:01,710
Mr. Kang. Don't do this.

703
00:59:01,909 --> 00:59:03,780
- Mr. Kang. - Stop it now.

704
00:59:06,809 --> 00:59:07,880
Gyeo Rye.

705
00:59:09,579 --> 00:59:11,150
Please stop now.

706
00:59:12,090 --> 00:59:13,119
Will you?

707
00:59:15,219 --> 00:59:16,320
Stop it!

708
00:59:20,900 --> 00:59:21,900
Stop!

709
00:59:29,400 --> 00:59:30,440
Stop it.

710
00:59:32,869 --> 00:59:36,309
That's exactly what he wants from you.

711
00:59:36,739 --> 00:59:38,279
Don't you know...

712
00:59:38,280 --> 00:59:40,719
how many people tried to stop you from becoming a murderer?

713
00:59:43,280 --> 00:59:45,849
So, stop it.

714
00:59:49,590 --> 00:59:50,630
Yoon Gyeo Rye.

715
00:59:51,190 --> 00:59:54,329
I couldn't find you anywhere.

716
00:59:54,599 --> 00:59:56,400
- What are you doing here? - Gosh.

717
00:59:58,099 --> 01:00:00,670
What are you doing here, you thugs?

718
01:00:07,079 --> 01:00:09,110
Hey. What are you doing here?

719
01:00:18,519 --> 01:00:20,420
Let me go. Gyeo Rye.

720
01:00:25,489 --> 01:00:26,789
Crazy punk.

721
01:00:27,800 --> 01:00:28,800
No.

722
01:00:44,909 --> 01:00:47,579
(If You Wish Upon Me)

723
01:00:47,719 --> 01:00:48,750
Do you know him?

724
01:00:49,250 --> 01:00:51,989
Thank you for everything. Let's go on our separate ways now.

725
01:00:52,519 --> 01:00:54,619
I'm here because Gyeo Rye asked.

726
01:00:55,389 --> 01:00:57,360
Don't give up like this.

727
01:00:58,190 --> 01:01:00,900
I think my wish came true.

728
01:01:01,730 --> 01:01:03,500
You'll get quite a lot for insurance.

729
01:01:04,000 --> 01:01:07,940
Can you give us a sneeze?

730
01:01:08,070 --> 01:01:10,610
Do you want to be my family?

731
01:01:11,369 --> 01:01:13,210
I want to ask Team Genie...

732
01:01:13,840 --> 01:01:16,210
my last wish.
